snippet.title: ROUTINE Re-reveal Announcement
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam to stay up to date!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/606160/ROUTINE/

Lunar Software and Raw Fury have teamed up to bring Routine to PC, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, and Game Pass! Explore an abandoned Lunar base and uncover a deadly mystery that could cost you everything.
